## ğŸ§  Features

- ğŸ•¸ **Real-time Craigslist scraping** via headless Chromium & Selenium
- ğŸ§½ **Smart attribute parsing** (model, size, year, etc.) using BeautifulSoup
- â³ **Waits for JavaScript-rendered content** before parsing
- â— **Keyword de-spamming**: Ignores those icky keyword-stuffed blocks
- ğŸ§  **False negative reducers**: Parses even when Craigslist uses funky formatting
- ğŸ“¢ **Automatic Discord alerts** via webhook
- ğŸ¤– **Logs everything** it finds, skips, or posts
- ğŸ§¯ **Fails gracefully** on slow pages, missing elements, or Razor scooters

